	(text "6 Servo PWM\n5 UART (1, 2, 3, 4, 5) (Telemetry radio connects to UART)\n2 I2C (0, 1) (I2C-1 can be either I2C-1 or UART-4) (I2C0 is in 400kb/s mode)\n2 SPI Buses (0, 1)\n2 GPIO (24, 25) (DIO, PWM, AIO, UART6, I2C2)\n1 Can Bus (CAN3)\n1 Remote Bypass Switch (Pin 32, Pulled Up, Active Low)"
